  "title": "Sales Executive (FMCG)",
  "description": "<ol>\n  <li><strong>Sales Team Leadership:</strong>Plan, direct, and monitor sales team activities to achieve established targets.<br>\nDevelop sales plans, strategies, and campaigns.<br>\nManage day-to-day sales team operations to implement the company’s overall sales strategy.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Sales Performance Management:</strong>Prepare sales forecasts and budgets.<br>\nMonitor sales volume, revenues, and costs against forecasts.<br>\nIdentify problem areas and reallocate resources to improve overall sales team performance.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Customer Relationship Building:</strong>Proactively develop win-win sales strategies with new and potential customers.<br>\nBuild strong relationships with suppliers and negotiate favorable conditions.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Market Insights and Strategy:</strong>Understand customer and market needs.<br>\nProvide necessary information to drive further strategy and product development.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Holistic Strategy Contribution:</strong>Contribute to sales, marketing, customer relations, advertising, pricing, and distribution strategies.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Sales Team Support:</strong>Coach sales team members on technical aspects, marketing, and sales techniques.<br>\nEnsure adherence to procedures and standards to achieve sales targets.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Effective Pricing and Communication:</strong>Offer competitive pricing to win new business and sustain growth.<br>\nMaintain good communication with internal stakeholders.<br>\n</li>\n</ol>",
